parameters: To think this is actually Ainoa...
Oi, what do you mean by that?
You really went through a lot.
When you ended up alone, that is.
I was rather saddened by the lack of anything.
Well, let's get back to the point.
Maybe you shouldn't stay here for too long?
Since it brings up bad memories and all.
But since you're here, I can rest easy.
What's this all of a sudden.
...You seem to be in a good mood.
When you were fighting Kaamos in Virea,
you became super strong all of a sudden.
If you're always like that all the time
I can always rely on you!
At that time, I was so angry...
The \C[3]Wand of Dregs\C[0] regains its light...
This stone statue resembles Miss Tahati...
